OL,3,CJohn Swinney to tell Edinburgh rally
OL,4,Cof 'prize' of Scottish independence
OL,6,FThe "prize" of Scottish independence
OL,7,Fis up for grabs when Scots go to the
OL,8,Fpolls in May, John Swinney has
OL,9,Finsisted.
OL,11,FHe will insist that leaving the
OL,12,F"broken" Westminster system could see
OL,13,Fenergy bills reduced for Scots while
OL,14,Fthe NHS would be "protected" from
OL,15,Fpossible privatisation.
OL,17,FHe made the claims ahead of a major
OL,18,Fpro-independence march and rally
OL,19,Ftaking place in the Scottish capital
OL,20,Fon Saturday.
OL,26,@nD@EOUnD@KO]tD@AOUtD@HO]vD@ROUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
