OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774663388
OL,3,CJohn Swinney to tell Edinburgh rally
OL,4,Cof 'prize' of Scottish independence
OL,6,FThe First Minister and SNP leader will
OL,7,Faddress crowds at the event in
OL,8,FEdinburgh, with Succession star Brian
OL,9,FCox also due to speak.
OL,11,FSpeaking ahead of Saturday's event,
OL,12,Forganised by campaigners at Believe in
OL,13,FScotland, Mr Swinney said: "The
OL,14,FWestminster establishment is broken.
OL,15,FAnd it is Scotland that is paying the
OL,16,Fprice.
OL,18,F"In one of the most energy-rich
OL,19,Fcountries in the world, people pay
OL,20,Fsome of the highest energy bills in
OL,21,FEurope.
OL,26,@uD@\OUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774663388
OL,3,CJohn Swinney to tell Edinburgh rally
OL,4,Cof 'prize' of Scottish independence
OL,6,F"It does not add up. And yet it is the
OL,7,Freality for people right across this
OL,8,Fcountry. Westminster has failed."
OL,10,FAdding that "Westminster is broken",
OL,11,Fhe said his party's job was now "to
OL,12,Finspire people with a vision for
OL,13,FScotland that is better than what
OL,14,FWestminster can offer".
OL,16,FHe added that the SNP must "show how
OL,17,Fwe can use the powers of independence
OL,18,Fnot just to prevent the worst failures
OL,19,Fof Westminster but to build something
OL,20,Fbetter for Scotland".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@aO]rD@MOUrD@cO]sD@aOUvD@VO]xD@
OL,26,A\OU|D@TO]
