OL,3,CJohn Swinney to tell Edinburgh rally
OL,4,Cof 'prize' of Scottish independence
OL,6,FMr Swinney said this could be "a
OL,7,Fcountry with lower energy bills, where
OL,8,Four NHS is protected from the threat
OL,9,Fof Westminster privatisation, where
OL,10,Four industry is protected and jobs
OL,11,Fsecured".
OL,13,FThe First Minister declared: "That is
OL,14,Fwhat independence means for Scotland `
OL,15,Fand that is the prize that is before
OL,16,Fus on May 7 with an SNP majority."
OL,26,@nD@_OUsD@HO]uD@^OUxD@bO]
