OL,3,CJohn Swinney to tell Edinburgh rally
OL,4,Cof 'prize' of Scottish independence
OL,6,FThe SNP leader believes an overall
OL,7,Fmajority for his party will force the
OL,8,FUK Government to allow a second
OL,9,FScottish independence referendum to
OL,10,Ftake place.
OL,12,FThe previous vote, held back in 2014,
OL,13,Fcame after the SNP won an historic
OL,14,FHolyrood majority in the 2011 election.
OL,16,FScottish Greens, meanwhile, believe
OL,17,Ftheir MSPs can make up part of a pro-
OL,18,Findependence majority in the 129-seat
OL,19,FParliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
