PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774663388
OL,3,CJohn Swinney to tell Edinburgh rally
OL,4,Cof 'prize' of Scottish independence
OL,6,FCo-leaders Gillian Mackay and Ross
OL,7,FGreer will also be among those
OL,8,Faddressing the rally.
OL,10,FMs Mackay said that "every vote" for
OL,11,Fher party in the May 7 election "is a
OL,12,Fvote for a fairer, greener and
OL,13,Findependent Scotland".
OL,15,FShe added: "Every poll shows that it
OL,16,Fis those Green votes that can make the
OL,17,Fdifference in terms of securing a pro-
OL,18,Findependence majority in May.
OL,26,@rD@UOUrD@`O]sD@aOUuD@UO]wD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
