PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774663388
OL,3,CJohn Swinney to tell Edinburgh rally
OL,4,Cof 'prize' of Scottish independence
OL,6,F"With Labour failing on all fronts and
OL,7,Fthe prospect of Nigel Farage in
OL,8,FDowning Street, it is more crucial
OL,9,Fthan ever that we take our future into
OL,10,Four own hands.
OL,12,F"We cannot continue allowing decisions
OL,13,Fto be made for us by far and remote
OL,14,Fgovernments who are all too happy to
OL,15,Fignore Scotland.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
