OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774663388
OL,3,CJohn Swinney to tell Edinburgh rally
OL,4,Cof 'prize' of Scottish independence
OL,6,F"If our parliament loses our pro-
OL,7,Findependence majority, then we risk
OL,8,FLabour, Tories and Reform putting up
OL,9,Feven more hurdles and barriers, and
OL,10,Flaunching even more attacks on
OL,11,Fdevolution."
OL,13,FSpeaking to the Press Association
OL,14,Fahead of the march, Scottish Tory
OL,15,Fleader Russell Findlay said: "It would
OL,16,Fbe very easy to dismiss John Swinney
OL,17,Fwalking around waving flags as a bit
OL,18,Fof a joke, but it's not a joke.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@LO]wD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774663388
OL,3,CJohn Swinney to tell Edinburgh rally
OL,4,Cof 'prize' of Scottish independence
OL,6,F"We've already heard what he's said,
OL,7,Fhe thinks he's going to win a
OL,8,Fmajority, he's going to say that will
OL,9,Fgive him a mandate for another
OL,10,Fdivisive and damaging referendum.
OL,12,F"Then he's talking about being the
OL,13,Fprime minister of an independent
OL,14,FScotland in five years' time.
OL,16,F"So it's not a joke ` it's not a
OL,17,Flaughing matter."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOUyD@QO]
